	that there shall be no termination of any bona fide claim for indemnification that has been delivered to the indemnifying Person in accordance with the terms of this Agreement with respect to such a representation, warranty, covenant or agreement prior to its expiration date and such representation, warranty, covenant or agreement shall survive until such claim is fully and finally resolved.







	(b)



