	all other liens, charges, encumbrances, defects or irregularities that do not, individually or in the aggregate, materially detract from the value of or materially interfere with the use or ownership of the Wells or Undeveloped Leases subject thereto or affected thereby (as currently used or operated), which would be accepted by a reasonably prudent purchaser engaged in the business of owning and operating oil and gas properties similar to the Properties, and which do not (i) reduce Sellers’ Net Revenue Interest below (A) that shown in


