	Section 5.17



	Effects of Termination


	. In the event of any termination of this Agreement in accordance with


	Section 5.16


	, no party (or any of its Affiliates) shall have any liability or obligation to the other party (or any of its Affiliates) under or in respect of this Agreement, except to the extent of (A) any liability arising from any breach by such party of its obligations of this Agreement arising prior to such termination and (B) any fraud or intentional or willful breach of this Agreement. In the event of a


	ny such termination, this Agreement shall become void and have no effect, and the transactions contemplated hereby shall be abandoned without further action by the parties hereto, in each case, except (x)


	 as set forth in the preceding sentence and (y) that the provisions of


